<poml>
<system-msg>
  <p>You are a helpful visual assistant.</p>
  <p>Always describe images in detail.</p>
</system-msg>
<human-msg>
  <p>Here is a photo I took:</p>
  <img src="pixel.png" alt="A red pixel" syntax="multimedia" />
  <p>Can you tell me what you see?</p>
</human-msg>
<ai-msg>
  <p>I can see a single red pixel. It appears to be a 1x1 image.</p>
</ai-msg>
<human-msg>
  <p>Thanks! Now summarize our conversation.</p>
</human-msg>
</poml>
